query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(t1 s) NoMergeJoin(s t1 tq1) NoMergeJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b1) */ select count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('cucumber-java',
'flv') AND s.site_name = 'stackoverflow'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%me'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id;
